	   <tr><td colspan=2>Agi: no effect on dodge, dodge is a skill and it will come into play based on your skill value.<br><br>Dex: no effect on channeling, channeling is a skill and it will come into play based on your skill value (with additional mod for AA)<br><br>Tried and tested, no noticable difference between high stat mode and low stat mode in these particular stats.<br><br>Kamlatir, <br>60 Grave Lord of Far Seekers<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
