	   <tr><td colspan=2>For a somewhat out of the way option, and IMHO at your level a very safe option - start rampaging through the Warrens.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br><br>You can get a bind right outside the dungeon, and the little runts drop a lot of weapons and armor that you can sell for pp.  Before your faction is dubious to the Heretics you can sell the stuff to the merchant in the druid circle, but eventually your faction will be good enough to sell right in Paineel.  The teeth quest may even give you ringmail to sell....<br><br>As a plus you raise your faction in Paineel which you will need to have at amiable to start your epic quest.  Might as well do it early while you still get some exp from the higher level mobs in the dungeon.  <br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
