	   <tr><td colspan=2>Alot of new people to the world of Norrath have been asking that question lately. There are several easy ways to raise cash.<br><br>1. If you have time to burn learn what the going rates of items are in the market zones on your server. Look for good deals and buy the item then sell the item for more than what you payed.<br><br>2. Collect items used in trade skills, eg Quality bear/cat/wolf pelts, spiderling silks and spider silks.<br><br>3. Hunt in dungeons these zones tend to drop more coin and fs weapons than outside zones.<br><br>I hope this helps you.<br>&nbsp;<br>Cannis 51st Ranger<br>Razer 50th Sk<br>Jeetkundo 20th Monk<br>Mikaraz 30th Warrior<br></td></tr>
