	   <tr><td colspan=2>At lvl 51 you get Resistant, adds 10 to all resists and duration gets longer each level.<br><br>At 52 or so you get Fearless, 18 seconds on immunity to fear spells (including Dragon Fear).&nbsp;&nbsp;It's very useless so I never even added a hotkey for it.<br><br>At lvl 55 you get Unholy Aura, it gives about 50% increase in HT and changes to resists to desease based from magic based.  The resistance check is the best part, but be careful as this has gotten me complete resists too when I wasn't thinking and used discipline HT against desease immune MOBs.<br><br>Leach Cures is next and heals you equal to every point of damage you do to a MOB.  I'm looking forward to this Discipline at lvl 60 though.<br><br>Neptunis Rex<br>lvl 55 DE Revenant<br>&nbsp;<br>Neptunis Rex<br>lvl 56 DE Revenant</td></tr>
